data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath located in the desirable Historic Haymount. Kitchen is equip with Butcher Block countertops as well as Stainless Steel Appliances. The open concept kitchen area is great for entertaining! This home also features a separate office as well as a mud room. All appliances do convey with the home, which includes the washer and dryer. Even with current interest rates being unusually high- this interest rate is assumable at 4.875% for a funding fee of .5% on this home! Please contact USAA for further details.
